### OTP API quick tests (JetBrains HTTP Client)

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000
@testEmail = your_email@example.com
@otpCode = 123456

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: application/json

### Send OTP (direct send, returns SMTP errors if any)
POST {{baseUrl}}/send-otp/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{testEmail}}"
}

### Send OTP (background mode)
POST {{baseUrl}}/send-otp/?send_in_background=true
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{testEmail}}"
}

### Verify OTP (replace otpCode with email OTP)
POST {{baseUrl}}/verify-otp/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{testEmail}}",
  "otp": "{{otpCode}}"
}

### Verify OTP with invalid code (negative test)
POST {{baseUrl}}/verify-otp/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{testEmail}}",
  "otp": "000000"
}

